Characters have some sort of automatic interaction at times.

The flat chested wolf does this arf sound and nips your fingers, that was incredibly cute (apparently the male model can bite them off).
There is probably more than that I didn't come across, since it also seemed to be exclusive to one pose specifically.
They also crawl their toes and some other nice details.
Sadly no physical ears for some reason, that should really be a no brainer.
It doesn't use physical mesh, so there is no detailed skin deformation like in VAM.
The fetish options are a nice bonus, it has macro/micro, water sports and milking (just particles).
I don't think its worth the 10€ yet but its on a good track since it focuses on interaction instead of high poly count or ultra high texture resolutions.
